'''Operation Kino e-Sports''' is a Brazilian multi-gaming organization.

== History ==
In January 2016, it was announced that [[JAYOB e-Sports]] had transferred its roster and coach to '''Operation Kino'''. With this transfer, the JAYOB organization could continue sponsoring other CBLOL teams, such as [[Keyd Stars]].

